Package: useful
Title: Some functions I'm always using in empirical climate econometrics research
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Thomas", "Bearpark", , "t.bearpark@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A bunch of helpful functions for running fixed effects regressions, 
    plotting their outputs. Heavily dependent on the feols package. 
